<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This is an interim update to the statutory list of policies for schools. This document will be reviewed again in 2019 as part of a wider review of our guidance.</p>

<p>This is for:</p>

<ul>
  <li>school leaders</li>
  <li>governing bodies</li>
  <li>proprietors of independent schools</li>
  <li>local authorities</li>
</ul>

<p>It applies to all schools.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

    </div>

